{"tid":612579,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"王者再臨  Motorola發佈超薄大熒幕摺機","createTime":"2018-04-01T03:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T04:02:21.000Z","uid":77956,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c13844a6a83b374eadc270bccdd3c1e557cd2a08","tid":612579,"uid":77956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:20:42.000Z","msg":"在多年前的MicroTAC以後，摺機世界一直沒有夠份量的新力軍。就在年初，摩托羅拉在北美宣佈摺機家族的重量級新成員&mdash;Star tac。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b3/MotorolaStarTAC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fb%2Fb3%2FMotorolaStarTAC.jpg&h=14eff708&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nStar tac輕巧非常，只重94g，機身雖小卻有劃時代的功能。機身搭配了一塊大大的LED螢幕，且具有最新的SMS功能，能傳送文字訊息。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.slashgear.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/motorola_startac_nostalgia_0-580x418.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.slashgear.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F07%2Fmotorola_startac_nostalgia_0-580x418.jpg&h=da6d00dc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n此外，此機亦有獨一無二的震動功能，讓你在無聲無息中知會電話的到來。多元的功能表，讓你隨心、快捷的選擇各項功能，機側更設智慧鍵，讓你一按即達通訊錄，無需從目錄選單進入。大膽採用了最新式的lithium-ion鋰電池，不必再受電池記憶放應的困擾。 <br />\n<br />\n本機在一月已於美國上市，單機售價約$1,000美金。"},{"pid":"cffa3d2b2c44600f54761b29f151b90148bd2c2f","tid":612579,"uid":139150,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:23:26.000Z","msg":"好難想像以前嘅人會覺得震憾 希望未來我地電話有更大嘅advancement"},{"pid":"bc0b0d2f0c7e8c2c2d22b3cdabddc3cd2edadc0c","tid":612579,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為真"},{"pid":"4e30cb439360374a070801175088e78a78617626","tid":612579,"uid":59639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:54:15.000Z","m